HEADWORD: Egg-glass
<hw>Egg"-glass`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small sandglass,
running about three minutes, for marking time in boiling eggs; also, a
small glass for holding an egg, at table.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Egghot</ent>⟦br⟧
